FIG. 9 is a block view showing a key portion of the slide door control unit;


FIG. 10 is a timing chart for explaining an operation of a speed calculating portion;


FIG. 11 is a flow chart showing the first half of the process of an automatic door opening control;


FIG. 12 is a flow chart showing the second half of the process of an automatic door opening control;


FIG. 13 is a flow chart showing the process of an automatic door closing control;


FIG. 14 is a flow chart showing the process of a manual/automatic select control;


FIG. 15 is a flow chart showing the process of a modification of the automatic door opening control shown in FIG. 12;


FIG. 16 is a flow chart showing the process of another modification of the automatic door opening control shown in FIG. 12; and


FIG. 17 is a flow chart showing the process of yet another modification of the automatic door opening control shown in FIG. 12.
